                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/6291: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China (<persName type="to">Johnson</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-05-20T16:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 20, 1933—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>174. Your 455, May 19, 4 p.m. If United Press accounts of this incident are
                    approximately accurate, Department feels that on the basis of this incident
                    and/or any other similar incidents a protest by the diplomatic body or Ministers
                    of the leading powers would be in order. You should take no initiative in the
                    matter but in case the question is raised by one of your colleagues you are
                    authorized in your discretion to take, as of your own conception, that
                    position.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
